Here is a textfile for learning.

1) Install Bower
2) With Bower Install things like Bootstrap etc.
3) Set up files for main.scss

// Import Bootstrap files
@import
    "../bower_components/bootstrap-sass/assets/stylesheets/bootstrap.scss",
    "../bower_components/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css",
    // Google fonts
    "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro:200,300,400,600,700,300italic,400italic"
;



// Override any Bootstrap variables

// Import partials (defaults to `_sass`)
@import
    "header",
    "content",
    "footer"
;

4) duplicate bower components into _site
5) set up bower init